WEBVTT

01:25.980 --> 01:34.920
[LIVE UP TO YOUR YOUTH]

01:35.330 --> 01:37.930
[Episode 25]

01:38.450 --> 01:39.259
Like I said,

01:40.090 --> 01:41.759
every play has its own fate.

01:42.340 --> 01:47.070
[The Late Love Filming Team]

01:43.120 --> 01:44.979
No matter how unacceptable it is,

01:45.850 --> 01:47.050
you have to accept it.

01:49.930 --> 01:51.330
I just don't understand.

01:51.870 --> 01:57.160
[The Late Love Filming Team]

01:52.500 --> 01:53.500
How come everything seems

01:53.500 --> 01:55.030
to have changed overnight?

01:56.840 --> 01:57.740
Actually,

01:58.900 --> 01:59.880
every change

01:59.950 --> 02:01.480
leaves a trace.

02:01.570 --> 02:02.480
Come on, sit down.

02:02.480 --> 02:02.930
Sit.

02:02.760 --> 02:07.860
[The Late Love Filming Team]

02:08.250 --> 02:10.449
Ever since he asked us to take out a loan,

02:10.630 --> 02:11.470
we've been having doubts

02:11.470 --> 02:12.970
the entire time, haven't we?

02:12.970 --> 02:13.860
However,

02:14.240 --> 02:15.460
our obsession

02:15.460 --> 02:16.470
with this project

02:16.560 --> 02:18.750
has outweighed all the uncertainties.

02:18.750 --> 02:20.410
If we were to start over again,

02:20.520 --> 02:22.150
we'd still have to
go with the same option.

02:22.150 --> 02:22.620
So,

02:23.780 --> 02:25.520
we must face the consequences.

02:26.870 --> 02:27.829
In fact,

02:28.300 --> 02:29.510
in one's life,

02:30.000 --> 02:31.329
if there are a few things

02:31.520 --> 02:33.000
that one knows to be fiery pits

02:33.000 --> 02:34.460
but still gladly jumps in,

02:34.650 --> 02:37.280
it's not necessarily a bad thing, is it?

02:38.280 --> 02:39.800
Director! Director!

02:40.010 --> 02:42.100
["The Late Love"
Filming Team–Producer's Office]

02:41.340 --> 02:42.260
Director,

02:42.520 --> 02:44.650
the entire crew is asking me for money.

02:45.030 --> 02:47.090
My pager is exploding with messages.

02:47.370 --> 02:48.150
I dare not return

02:48.150 --> 02:49.350
a single call.

02:49.680 --> 02:51.280
What should we do about this?

02:52.579 --> 02:53.329
Pay them.

02:53.490 --> 02:57.170
[The Late Love Filming Team]

02:53.630 --> 02:55.329
We must pay them up.

02:56.030 --> 02:57.430
Come home with me now.

02:57.710 --> 02:59.620
I'll take money out
from my deposit account.

02:59.620 --> 02:59.970
Okay.

02:59.970 --> 03:00.800
Do some calculation.

03:00.800 --> 03:02.060
Find out what payments

03:02.180 --> 03:04.030
must be made by the end of this month.

03:04.030 --> 03:04.780
Okay, got it.

03:15.080 --> 03:15.620
Hello?

03:16.280 --> 03:17.530
Hello, Zhuang Zhuang.

03:17.530 --> 03:19.300
I was busy just now. What's up?

03:19.680 --> 03:21.680
How's the movie preparation going?

03:22.280 --> 03:23.010
Pretty good.

03:23.460 --> 03:24.920
The staff are all in place.

03:25.240 --> 03:26.770
Once the next loan arrives,

03:26.860 --> 03:28.090
we'll start shooting.

03:28.090 --> 03:29.150
Director Weng said

03:29.370 --> 03:31.430
the cast all think highly of the script.

03:31.430 --> 03:33.310
That Hong Kong celebrity you're fond of

03:33.310 --> 03:34.440
will come do a cameo.

03:34.520 --> 03:36.240
I'll get you an autograph then.

03:36.240 --> 03:36.920
Okay.

03:38.360 --> 03:40.079
Mr. Ye and your mom must be overjoyed

03:40.079 --> 03:41.410
to have you home, right?

03:45.680 --> 03:47.079
When are you coming back?

03:47.130 --> 03:47.780
I'll go pick you up.

03:47.780 --> 03:49.840
I need to stay here for another while.

03:50.310 --> 03:52.770
Will you make it in time
for the competition?

03:52.900 --> 03:54.340
Yes, I will. Don't worry.

03:55.870 --> 03:56.329
Okay.

03:57.180 --> 03:59.370
Remember to practice singing
when you have time.

03:59.370 --> 04:00.880
Also, come back early.

04:01.000 --> 04:01.780
When you're sure of the time,

04:01.780 --> 04:02.560
just let me know.

04:02.560 --> 04:04.420
I'll check on the tickets for you.

04:04.800 --> 04:05.950
Okay, I got it.

04:06.130 --> 04:07.400
I have to hang up now.

04:07.430 --> 04:09.130
T-Take care of yourself.

04:10.230 --> 04:10.700
Okay.

04:21.769 --> 04:22.560
We understand

04:22.560 --> 04:24.090
how you must feel right now.

04:24.220 --> 04:25.420
But the cancer treatment process

04:25.420 --> 04:26.480
is indeed lengthy.

04:27.040 --> 04:28.100
In particular, your mother's condition

04:28.100 --> 04:30.160
is more complicated than we thought.

04:30.360 --> 04:31.610
I'm a daughter too.

04:31.950 --> 04:32.890
See, with you back home,

04:32.890 --> 04:34.350
your mother is very happy.

04:34.600 --> 04:36.430
This is of great help to her condition.

04:36.430 --> 04:37.270
So, as her daughter,

04:37.270 --> 04:38.100
don't be disheartened.

04:38.100 --> 04:40.500
Spend more time with her
and encourage her.

04:41.930 --> 04:42.659
Stay strong.

04:43.130 --> 04:44.510
Let's all do our best together.

04:44.510 --> 04:45.770
-I got it.
-Go back now.

04:46.170 --> 04:49.920
[No smoking in public areas]

05:06.210 --> 05:08.570
[The Late Love]

05:19.370 --> 05:20.300
Don't be afraid.

05:21.000 --> 05:22.260
I've asked the doctor.

05:22.660 --> 05:24.010
You'll fall asleep after the anesthesia.

05:24.010 --> 05:26.070
Then all will be fine when you wake up.

05:26.390 --> 05:27.450
With you by my side,

05:28.300 --> 05:29.960
I definitely won't be afraid.

05:31.950 --> 05:33.070
I'll go get some hot water

05:33.070 --> 05:34.000
to help you wash up.

05:34.000 --> 05:34.930
There's no rush.

05:37.130 --> 05:38.540
Fetch me my bag

05:38.540 --> 05:39.470
from the closet.

05:45.310 --> 05:46.370
It's the one on top.

05:51.250 --> 05:52.310
What's in it?

05:56.420 --> 05:57.840
Previously,

05:58.370 --> 05:59.830
when I was feeling better,

06:00.270 --> 06:01.930
I made you some clothes.

06:09.890 --> 06:11.250
I made this costume for you

06:11.250 --> 06:12.560
to wear on stage.

06:23.890 --> 06:24.780
And this one...

06:25.430 --> 06:27.480
is for you to wear on your wedding.

06:59.120 --> 06:59.900
Is it pretty?

07:03.130 --> 07:03.690
Yes.

07:13.000 --> 07:15.400
I've noticed you've gotten thinner again.

07:15.500 --> 07:16.550
I'm not sure

07:16.950 --> 07:18.880
if these dresses will fit you well.

07:19.270 --> 07:21.000
Alter them yourself if needed.

07:24.000 --> 07:24.670
No, I won't.

07:25.800 --> 07:26.740
I'll wait till you recover

07:26.740 --> 07:27.870
before I try them on.

07:28.180 --> 07:28.980
If they don't fit,

07:28.980 --> 07:30.710
I'll have you alter them for me.

07:37.600 --> 07:38.240
Okay.

07:40.180 --> 07:41.510
I'll alter them for you.

08:28.360 --> 08:31.510
The last time you lay beside me

08:32.600 --> 08:34.159
in a hospital bed like this,

08:36.100 --> 08:38.059
you were a chubby,

08:38.360 --> 08:39.500
soft little baby

08:40.390 --> 08:43.500
who smiled at the sight of me.

08:46.530 --> 08:47.660
Little did I imagine

08:48.600 --> 08:50.310
you'd grow up so fast

08:50.480 --> 08:52.080
into an extraordinary lady.

08:54.600 --> 08:56.250
You've only seen a fraction

08:56.250 --> 08:57.510
of what I'm capable of.

09:00.910 --> 09:02.890
After you're discharged from the hospital,

09:02.890 --> 09:03.650
I'll show you

09:03.650 --> 09:05.350
the movie I took part in.

09:07.010 --> 09:08.870
I played a great Shanghai singer.

09:09.000 --> 09:10.060
Splendid, I'd say.

09:13.370 --> 09:14.950
I also designed a dress,

09:15.360 --> 09:17.420
but the drawing was nearly snatched.

09:18.250 --> 09:20.110
Luckily, I fought and got it back.

09:20.720 --> 09:21.200
I'm waiting

09:21.200 --> 09:23.000
for you to make that dress for me.

09:31.910 --> 09:33.720
What was the song

09:33.720 --> 09:34.770
you said I'd smile at

09:34.770 --> 09:35.970
whenever you sang it?

09:36.360 --> 09:37.550
Sing it to me again.

09:42.720 --> 09:46.630
Go to sleep,

09:47.550 --> 09:51.410
my dear baby.

09:52.240 --> 09:55.840
Sleep tight,

09:56.650 --> 09:59.860
Mommy loves you.

10:01.460 --> 10:05.700
Go to sleep,

10:06.650 --> 10:09.820
my dear baby.

10:13.750 --> 10:14.250
Uncle,

10:14.960 --> 10:16.820
if you're feeling unwell lately,

10:17.120 --> 10:17.790
just let me

10:17.790 --> 10:19.340
do your bidding.

10:19.870 --> 10:21.080
I'll keep the accounts

10:21.080 --> 10:22.530
clear and show them

10:22.670 --> 10:24.070
to you on a regular basis.

10:24.200 --> 10:25.440
If I have questions,

10:25.500 --> 10:26.830
I'll ask you for advice.

10:27.460 --> 10:28.150
Okay, okay.

10:30.150 --> 10:31.000
I trust you.

10:34.600 --> 10:36.490
Why don't you give me a smile?

10:36.600 --> 10:38.260
Because I'm still feeling...

10:38.820 --> 10:40.010
a bit worried.

10:40.320 --> 10:41.100
Look at you.

10:42.390 --> 10:44.240
It's the same old problem again.

10:44.870 --> 10:47.310
Cao Ye, I'm not criticizing you.

10:48.050 --> 10:49.790
But look out on the streets.

10:51.010 --> 10:52.500
Everyone's mind

10:52.520 --> 10:54.250
is far from simple.

10:54.630 --> 10:55.410
Who isn't

10:55.410 --> 10:57.200
sharp as a tack?

10:58.010 --> 10:59.870
You get bullied when you are weak.

11:00.630 --> 11:02.130
But when you are strong,

11:02.500 --> 11:04.770
everyone will smile at you.

11:08.270 --> 11:09.270
Wake up

11:10.270 --> 11:11.200
from your dream.

11:17.100 --> 11:17.770
Cui,

11:19.010 --> 11:20.220
thank you so much

11:20.700 --> 11:23.030
for all you've done for me
over these days.

11:23.580 --> 11:24.100
Ranran,

11:25.130 --> 11:27.190
are you sure you won't reconsider it?

11:28.840 --> 11:29.980
It's a wonderful role

11:29.980 --> 11:31.310
of a wonderful project.

11:31.370 --> 11:33.150
Everyone's fighting tooth and nail for it.

11:33.150 --> 11:34.080
See, you've just

11:34.270 --> 11:36.010
embarked on the journey
to a bright future.

11:36.010 --> 11:36.410
Why...

11:36.790 --> 11:38.410
why do you have to quit?

11:38.750 --> 11:39.520
Cui,

11:40.820 --> 11:42.130
I remember you saying

11:42.820 --> 11:45.080
that good luck only favors the capable.

11:47.290 --> 11:48.750
I don't think I'm capable enough

11:48.750 --> 11:50.220
to embrace such good luck.

11:50.770 --> 11:52.130
Even if I do,

11:52.630 --> 11:53.890
it won't serve me well.

11:54.340 --> 11:56.030
If I keep moving on like this,

11:57.240 --> 11:58.080
I'm afraid I'll really

11:58.080 --> 11:58.960
forget who I am.

12:01.120 --> 12:02.450
Chu Caiyuan

12:02.720 --> 12:03.850
is a married man,

12:03.910 --> 12:05.910
yet he's still looking for affairs.

12:05.960 --> 12:07.690
-I really think...
-He and I...

12:08.250 --> 12:10.310
will never ever get in contact again.

12:11.510 --> 12:12.640
It's all in the past.

12:16.810 --> 12:18.350
L-Let's not talk about him.

12:38.340 --> 12:39.600
For the sake of acting,

12:40.480 --> 12:41.340
I've suffered,

12:42.530 --> 12:43.860
swallowed grievances,

12:44.510 --> 12:45.460
and complained.

12:47.750 --> 12:48.740
But, Cui,

12:50.870 --> 12:52.870
if everyone in this industry

12:53.510 --> 12:55.910
needs to find a backer
before getting a job,

12:56.580 --> 12:58.110
don't you think it is wrong?

12:59.440 --> 13:00.930
If I rise to fame from this,

13:01.890 --> 13:03.620
then which poor actress like me

13:04.120 --> 13:05.340
has lost her chance to play the part

13:05.340 --> 13:06.010
I've got?

13:08.550 --> 13:09.690
I understand...

13:10.130 --> 13:11.260
what you're saying.

13:11.960 --> 13:12.690
Ranran,

13:13.220 --> 13:14.880
you are really different now.

13:17.580 --> 13:19.110
I'm leaving this industry.

13:20.100 --> 13:21.200
That means we won't get to

13:21.200 --> 13:22.130
meet up as often.

13:22.840 --> 13:23.970
I pray for you to find

13:24.720 --> 13:26.380
a suitable path for yourself.

13:27.290 --> 13:29.270
Remember? In a previous auction,

13:30.390 --> 13:32.990
I couldn't get into character
however I tried.

13:33.200 --> 13:34.270
But I caught on to it right away

13:34.270 --> 13:35.890
as you gave me an instruction.

13:35.890 --> 13:37.080
Don't you think...

13:37.290 --> 13:38.950
you have a gift for directing?

13:42.410 --> 13:43.270
Thank you.

13:43.740 --> 13:44.370
Well...

13:44.790 --> 13:45.720
I'll try my best.

13:45.890 --> 13:46.860
I really mean it.

13:46.860 --> 13:47.360
Yeah.

13:50.290 --> 13:50.960
Ranran,

13:51.890 --> 13:52.940
what do you plan

13:53.530 --> 13:54.860
to do in the future then?

13:57.650 --> 13:59.450
I don't want to go back to Huzhou.

14:01.270 --> 14:02.740
Now, I have found a job

14:02.740 --> 14:04.070
as a preschool teacher.

14:05.170 --> 14:06.530
I'll live my life well.

14:08.670 --> 14:09.400
That's good.

14:10.750 --> 14:14.270
[Scouting photos] [Character settings]

14:11.870 --> 14:13.670
As part of the filming industry,

14:13.720 --> 14:15.580
it's heartbreaking to see it lose

14:15.840 --> 14:18.010
such a good, dedicated

14:18.550 --> 14:20.370
and hardworking actress.

14:20.930 --> 14:22.530
But as a good friend of yours,

14:22.820 --> 14:23.820
I'm happy for you.

14:24.630 --> 14:25.320
I'm glad...

14:26.030 --> 14:27.100
that your heart is still

14:27.100 --> 14:27.960
as pure as ever

14:28.270 --> 14:30.600
after a journey through this vanity fair.

14:33.000 --> 14:34.260
I'll also pray for you.

14:36.700 --> 14:37.960
I wish you all the best.

14:39.170 --> 14:39.900
Absolutely.

14:40.700 --> 14:41.600
That was an impression of me.

14:41.600 --> 14:42.500
Was it spot-on?

14:42.750 --> 14:43.410
Not really.

14:47.960 --> 14:48.710
Liangliang!

14:49.510 --> 14:50.040
Liang...

14:50.960 --> 14:52.730
Why are you still sleeping?

14:52.820 --> 14:53.460
Get up!

14:53.600 --> 14:54.600
Come cook with me.

14:54.670 --> 14:55.580
We'll have drinks later.

14:55.580 --> 14:56.440
Come on, get up.

14:56.820 --> 14:57.880
Alright, Zongbao.

14:57.980 --> 14:59.110
You go do your thing.

14:59.150 --> 15:00.950
Let me have some quiet time here.

15:03.250 --> 15:04.840
What's going on with you?

15:06.910 --> 15:09.740
You've been doing business with Xiaojun

15:09.740 --> 15:10.960
lately.

15:11.320 --> 15:11.770
Why...

15:12.270 --> 15:14.340
do you look so listless?

15:15.580 --> 15:16.710
Come on.

15:17.170 --> 15:18.080
I'm a grown man

15:18.080 --> 15:18.840
who has worked his tail off

15:18.840 --> 15:19.630
without earning even a penny.

15:19.630 --> 15:20.760
How could I be happy?

15:23.550 --> 15:26.200
So you're worried that Ranran
might suffer with you

15:26.200 --> 15:28.330
since you haven't made any money, huh?

15:28.720 --> 15:30.410
Enough. Drop this subject.

15:30.410 --> 15:31.630
Just go do your thing.

15:33.320 --> 15:35.050
You're not in the right state.

15:35.940 --> 15:36.410
Get up!

15:37.940 --> 15:39.250
I said get up! Did you hear?

15:39.250 --> 15:40.620
Just go do your thing.

15:40.620 --> 15:42.120
Leave me alone.

15:44.050 --> 15:45.130
Hey,

15:46.130 --> 15:48.220
look where I stand now.

15:49.050 --> 15:49.850
For one thing,

15:49.960 --> 15:51.770
I have no money.

15:52.650 --> 15:54.740
For another, I have no background.

15:55.030 --> 15:56.200
But think about it.

15:56.940 --> 15:58.140
My wife and I

15:58.320 --> 15:59.600
are living

16:00.290 --> 16:02.200
a more and more enjoyable life.

16:04.860 --> 16:05.670
Why is that?

16:11.620 --> 16:13.390
Then please explain to me

16:13.390 --> 16:14.790
why things are picking up

16:15.390 --> 16:16.350
for you

16:16.790 --> 16:18.030
and your wife.

16:18.170 --> 16:18.750
First,

16:20.480 --> 16:21.960
I have a sincere heart.

16:23.000 --> 16:23.460
Second,

16:24.370 --> 16:25.890
for my wife

16:26.630 --> 16:27.340
and son,

16:28.000 --> 16:30.080
I can work my fingers to the bone, right?

16:30.080 --> 16:30.610
Third...

16:30.890 --> 16:32.530
Alright, stop it.

16:32.630 --> 16:34.090
I have a sincere heart too,

16:34.120 --> 16:35.360
and I can also work hard.

16:35.360 --> 16:36.460
But I don't have money!

16:36.460 --> 16:37.420
How can hard work

16:37.620 --> 16:39.460
and a sincere heart
be compared with money?

16:39.460 --> 16:41.200
I want to help Ranran realize her dream.

16:41.200 --> 16:42.170
I hate to see her

16:42.170 --> 16:43.370
sitting in that Lincoln.

16:43.370 --> 16:45.170
But what can I do when I'm so poor?

16:45.790 --> 16:47.450
Okay, alright, I understand.

16:50.050 --> 16:50.780
Liangliang.

16:52.670 --> 16:55.030
You can't keep being like this.

16:56.460 --> 16:58.330
You are like a brother

16:58.770 --> 16:59.720
to us.

17:00.700 --> 17:01.320
However,

17:01.340 --> 17:03.350
in front of Ranran,

17:03.980 --> 17:05.900
you must act like a real man.

17:06.500 --> 17:08.550
How long have we known Ranran?

17:09.569 --> 17:11.770
You're well aware of what kind of person

17:11.940 --> 17:13.000
she is, aren't you?

17:14.000 --> 17:15.970
Don't obsess over

17:16.290 --> 17:17.810
what you need to become

17:17.810 --> 17:19.210
just to give her the best.

17:19.420 --> 17:20.680
You should think about

17:20.900 --> 17:22.300
what Ranran really needs

17:22.530 --> 17:23.589
in her inner heart.

17:28.290 --> 17:30.610
Try not to let your pride

17:31.240 --> 17:32.940
hold you back.

17:33.960 --> 17:34.550
Okay?

17:36.220 --> 17:37.420
Give it some thought.

17:39.290 --> 17:40.340
I'm going to cook.

17:40.720 --> 17:42.880
Love is conveyed through cooking.

17:44.020 --> 17:46.220
I'll let you know when the food's ready.

17:46.680 --> 17:48.280
We'll have drinks, alright?

18:13.020 --> 18:19.370
[Surgery in Progress]

18:19.440 --> 18:24.430
[Operating Theater]

18:24.480 --> 18:34.110
[Surgery in Progress]

18:34.170 --> 18:42.030
[Operating Theater]

18:39.350 --> 18:40.400
During surgery, we found

18:40.400 --> 18:41.460
the patient's tumor is so large

18:41.460 --> 18:41.960
that it is

18:41.960 --> 18:43.610
compressing an artery in the lungs.

18:43.610 --> 18:44.480
Continuing the operation

18:44.480 --> 18:45.380
would greatly increase health risks.

18:45.380 --> 18:46.700
So we had to terminate it.

18:46.700 --> 18:48.420
T-Then where do we go from here?

18:48.420 --> 18:48.830
Next,

18:48.830 --> 18:50.400
we will arrange
radiotherapy and chemotherapy

18:50.400 --> 18:51.200
for the patient

18:51.200 --> 18:52.480
to shrink the tumor.

18:52.610 --> 18:54.470
Only then can we devise new plans.

18:56.310 --> 19:00.150
[Operating Theater]

19:04.720 --> 19:08.670
[Operating Theater]

19:29.880 --> 19:34.640
[Chinese Folk Music]

19:33.110 --> 19:34.790
You have a solid foundation in singing.

19:34.790 --> 19:35.590
Rest assured, Mr. Zheng.

19:35.590 --> 19:36.030
I will

19:36.030 --> 19:37.760
practice as often as possible.

19:41.310 --> 19:42.640
Beijing is full of talented people.

19:42.640 --> 19:44.250
The competition will be very fierce.

19:44.250 --> 19:45.250
Can you handle it?

19:45.610 --> 19:46.210
Yes, I can.

19:46.780 --> 19:48.860
[Notice of participation
in the National Singer Competition]

19:50.220 --> 19:51.620
The finalist list is out.

19:51.750 --> 19:53.410
You made it to the finals.

19:53.460 --> 19:54.160
You are now

19:54.160 --> 19:56.420
getting closer and closer to your dream.

20:18.200 --> 20:18.900
Hello, this is

20:18.900 --> 20:22.430
the organizing committee
of the National Singer Competition.

20:22.700 --> 20:23.400
Hello,

20:23.400 --> 20:26.000
this is Zhuang Zhuang,
one of the contestants.

20:26.680 --> 20:27.140
Hello.

20:27.350 --> 20:28.510
How may I help you?

20:33.720 --> 20:35.180
I've decided to withdraw.

20:38.770 --> 20:39.920
Are you sure?

20:45.480 --> 20:46.280
Yes, I'm sure.

20:46.550 --> 20:47.680
Sorry for quitting.

21:58.590 --> 21:59.530
Hello.

22:00.010 --> 22:01.870
Zhuang Zhuang, it's me, Shengli.

22:01.920 --> 22:03.920
Why haven't I heard from you lately?

22:03.960 --> 22:05.090
Is everything okay?

22:07.180 --> 22:08.640
The shooting has started.

22:08.680 --> 22:09.410
Don't worry.

22:10.110 --> 22:11.880
Have you filmed the scenes
you told me about

22:11.880 --> 22:12.720
earlier?

22:13.770 --> 22:14.700
Yes, all of them.

22:15.110 --> 22:17.110
Everything's going very smoothly.

22:17.510 --> 22:19.680
Director Weng is amazing.

22:20.000 --> 22:21.640
I've been watching him turning texts

22:21.640 --> 22:22.660
into pictures.

22:23.010 --> 22:24.270
It's really exciting.

22:24.310 --> 22:25.000
That day, after shooting,

22:25.000 --> 22:26.790
he even asked me to watch the editing.

22:26.790 --> 22:28.610
I went to the editing room, took a look,

22:28.610 --> 22:29.870
and was really amazed.

22:30.530 --> 22:32.460
He also told me to stay with the crew

22:32.570 --> 22:34.590
to do some script revision work.

22:38.000 --> 22:40.260
What about you? When are you coming back?

22:40.330 --> 22:41.010
Won't

22:41.050 --> 22:42.850
the competition commence soon?

22:45.110 --> 22:46.000
I did some thinking

22:46.000 --> 22:47.220
and decided to quit.

22:50.110 --> 22:52.440
When I attended the preliminary contest,

22:52.460 --> 22:54.440
I found my rivals all highly professional

22:54.440 --> 22:55.500
and better than me.

22:55.830 --> 22:58.000
There's no point in going for the finals.

22:58.000 --> 22:59.330
Are you nervous or what?

23:00.610 --> 23:02.010
I'm sure all will be fine.

23:02.270 --> 23:03.550
You're an excellent singer.

23:03.550 --> 23:05.950
You'll definitely outperform the others.

23:11.500 --> 23:11.900
Hello?

23:14.880 --> 23:16.010
Hey, Zhuang Zhuang?

23:17.110 --> 23:18.640
Why don't you say anything?

23:19.700 --> 23:20.100
Are...

23:21.180 --> 23:22.910
A-Are you sure about quitting?

23:23.740 --> 23:25.070
But why, Zhuang Zhuang?

23:25.810 --> 23:27.530
W-Why are you withdrawing?

23:27.830 --> 23:29.110
We've stuck it out so long in Beijing

23:29.110 --> 23:31.040
just to fulfill our dreams, right?

23:32.030 --> 23:33.090
The two of us worked

23:33.550 --> 23:35.480
from dawn to dusk selling clothes,

23:35.810 --> 23:36.290
and...

23:36.440 --> 23:37.640
we even went to Russia

23:37.880 --> 23:39.080
to resell clothes.

23:39.440 --> 23:40.070
We made all that effort

23:40.070 --> 23:42.200
just to survive in Beijing, didn't we?

23:42.250 --> 23:44.350
You're only one step away
from realizing your dream now.

23:44.350 --> 23:46.080
Why are you suddenly giving up?

23:48.310 --> 23:49.570
Hello, Zhuang Zhuang?

23:50.440 --> 23:51.970
Did anything happen to you?

23:53.160 --> 23:55.050
I'll come find you, Zhuang Zhuang.

23:55.050 --> 23:56.480
No, nothing happened.

24:00.940 --> 24:02.190
I'm perfectly fine.

24:04.480 --> 24:06.740
The shooting of your movie
has finally begun.

24:06.740 --> 24:08.600
Make sure you fulfill your dream.

24:08.680 --> 24:09.400
Zhuang Zhuang,

24:09.400 --> 24:11.060
your dream is my dream as well.

24:12.160 --> 24:14.160
Thank you for always supporting me.

24:14.550 --> 24:15.610
I sincerely hope

24:16.830 --> 24:17.290
your dream

24:17.290 --> 24:18.740
will come to a good end.

24:21.310 --> 24:21.980
I've made up my mind

24:21.980 --> 24:22.770
to quit the competition.

24:22.770 --> 24:24.010
Don't try to persuade me anymore.

24:24.010 --> 24:24.960
Zhuang Zhuang...

24:24.960 --> 24:28.220
-Zhuang Zhuang, you must not quit...
-Focus on your movie.

25:28.480 --> 25:29.150
Excuse me.

25:29.400 --> 25:30.980
No one's at Meiqin Tailor Shop.

25:30.980 --> 25:32.240
Do you know where the owner

25:32.240 --> 25:33.050
and her family live?

25:33.050 --> 25:33.930
And you are?

25:35.140 --> 25:36.050
I'm looking for her daughter,

25:36.050 --> 25:36.480
Zhuang Zhuang.

25:36.480 --> 25:39.610
Their address is No. 8, 69th Alley,
Shamao River Street.

25:44.550 --> 25:45.400
Who is it?

25:45.650 --> 25:47.250
It's me, Xu Shengli.

25:48.660 --> 25:49.520
Zhuang Zhuang?

25:49.570 --> 25:50.940
It's me, Shengli.

25:52.900 --> 25:53.760
Zhuang Zhuang?

25:54.440 --> 25:56.100
Zhuang Zhuang, open the door.

25:59.680 --> 26:00.540
Zhuang Zhuang.

26:09.220 --> 26:10.080
Zhuang Zhuang,

26:10.940 --> 26:12.330
can we have a word?

26:13.510 --> 26:14.910
Has something happened?

26:15.480 --> 26:16.810
You can tell me about it.

26:18.070 --> 26:19.870
As for the singing competition,

26:20.610 --> 26:21.200
under no circumstances

26:21.200 --> 26:22.530
should you give up on it.

26:23.570 --> 26:24.640
That's your dream.

26:25.420 --> 26:26.680
If you quit, then...

26:27.440 --> 26:28.200
my dream won't

26:28.200 --> 26:29.600
have any meaning either.

26:55.410 --> 27:00.610
♪ Grow wild like spring grass ♪

27:01.980 --> 27:09.220
♪ I embrace the galaxy
in the gentle evening breeze ♪

27:09.870 --> 27:13.530
♪ The sky slowly brightens into dawn ♪

27:14.070 --> 27:16.490
♪ Let me sing a song ♪

27:17.360 --> 27:20.090
♪ Unyielding even in cracks ♪

27:21.080 --> 27:29.400
♪ Wild grass thrives
in the lushness of spring ♪

27:37.070 --> 27:42.830
♪ The breeze knows and the dew knows ♪

27:43.990 --> 27:49.030
♪ That hometown is not a shelter
one can hide in forever ♪

27:50.960 --> 27:52.870
♪ Under the towering city walls ♪

27:52.680 --> 27:53.680
Zhuangzhuang, do you remember

27:53.330 --> 27:56.730
♪ In a corner of the northern sea ♪

27:53.740 --> 27:55.340
when you recorded this song,

27:55.700 --> 27:57.500
you were thrilled, weren't you?

27:57.950 --> 27:59.440
♪ And in places
where the sun doesn't shine ♪

27:59.530 --> 28:00.890
Are you being too nervous?

27:59.970 --> 28:02.510
♪ I've lingered and rested ♪

28:01.160 --> 28:02.760
Or are you just stressed out?

28:03.200 --> 28:03.880
It's okay.

28:04.220 --> 28:05.310
I will always be with you.

28:04.580 --> 28:10.010
♪ Towards the light,
I straighten my back ♪

28:05.920 --> 28:07.810
The result really doesn't matter,

28:07.810 --> 28:09.740
but at least we need to give it a try.

28:11.290 --> 28:16.910
♪ I must touch the clouds
however high the sky is ♪

28:18.610 --> 28:23.160
♪ Though I drift in the wind,
my heart remains unshaken ♪

28:23.140 --> 28:24.290
You're Shengli, right?

28:24.270 --> 28:26.300
♪ A ray of light will eventually ♪

28:26.140 --> 28:27.010
Mr. Ye.

28:27.290 --> 28:28.180
♪ Shed on me ♪

28:30.700 --> 28:32.710
What are you doing in Wenzhou?

28:33.590 --> 28:35.120
I'm here for Zhuang Zhuang.

28:37.160 --> 28:38.360
Her mother goes to bed

28:38.790 --> 28:39.640
early.

28:39.750 --> 28:41.460
She hasn't rested well lately.

28:41.460 --> 28:42.920
Please stop knocking at the door.

28:42.920 --> 28:44.050
It might wake her up.

28:47.750 --> 28:48.610
How about this?

28:48.770 --> 28:50.590
Go to the entrance to the alley and sit

28:50.590 --> 28:51.550
there for a while.

28:51.550 --> 28:54.100
I'll get in there, check on Zhuang Zhuang,

28:54.530 --> 28:56.330
and meet up with you later. Okay?

28:57.140 --> 28:58.470
Yes, sure.

28:58.790 --> 28:59.350
Mr. Ye,

28:59.830 --> 29:01.680
do try to persuade Zhuang Zhuang.

29:01.680 --> 29:02.220
She must not

29:02.220 --> 29:03.950
quit the singing competition.

29:04.250 --> 29:04.880
Got it.

29:05.220 --> 29:06.220
Thank you, Mr. Ye.

29:48.350 --> 29:49.210
Thanks, Mr. Ye.

30:04.590 --> 30:05.140
Kiddo,

30:07.160 --> 30:08.960
I know what you must be thinking.

30:11.810 --> 30:14.270
But I don't think you can hide the truth
from him forever,

30:14.270 --> 30:16.000
judging from how much he cares.

30:21.840 --> 30:23.640
I remember back in my childhood,

30:25.310 --> 30:27.510
when you first got together
with my mom,

30:27.850 --> 30:29.450
you were working out of town.

30:31.590 --> 30:33.320
Suppose at that time, my mom...

30:35.210 --> 30:35.740
my mom told you

30:35.740 --> 30:37.700
something serious happened at home,

30:37.700 --> 30:38.700
what would you do?

30:40.070 --> 30:42.200
I would definitely leave everything behind

30:42.200 --> 30:44.330
and come back to keep your mom company.

30:47.640 --> 30:49.570
Shengli is the same kind of person.

30:58.310 --> 30:59.710
Now, he is actually doing

31:00.480 --> 31:02.070
what he has always,

31:04.250 --> 31:05.450
always aspired to do.

31:06.070 --> 31:07.600
It's very important to him,

31:09.810 --> 31:10.750
just like how important

31:10.750 --> 31:12.610
the singing competition is to me.

31:14.310 --> 31:15.640
When a chance is missed,

31:16.790 --> 31:18.250
it might never come again.

31:27.400 --> 31:28.510
If I told him what our family

31:28.510 --> 31:30.040
is going through right now,

31:32.180 --> 31:33.460
he would by no means

31:33.460 --> 31:34.590
let me face it alone.

31:37.440 --> 31:38.530
No matter what,

31:39.380 --> 31:41.160
you must not hurt his feelings.

31:42.640 --> 31:43.970
Because when some words

31:45.090 --> 31:45.880
are said, they will

31:45.880 --> 31:47.140
cause eternal damage.

31:48.220 --> 31:49.710
That will be harm

31:50.270 --> 31:51.480
to both of you.

31:56.140 --> 31:58.340
No matter what you choose in the future,

31:58.620 --> 32:00.420
you have accompanied each other

32:01.350 --> 32:03.220
and given for each other.

32:04.030 --> 32:06.030
There's affection between you two.

32:13.110 --> 32:15.040
I don't know what the future holds.

32:26.030 --> 32:26.560
Alright.

32:29.010 --> 32:30.940
I know just what to tell him.

33:21.160 --> 33:21.750
Mr. Ye.

33:24.270 --> 33:25.030
Shengli,

33:26.270 --> 33:28.240
Zhuang Zhuang can't go with you.

33:31.880 --> 33:32.650
Then, Mr. Ye,

33:32.670 --> 33:33.820
can I see her?

33:34.720 --> 33:36.580
H-Has something happened to her?

33:36.700 --> 33:37.550
B-But no matter what,

33:37.550 --> 33:39.610
she can't give up on the competition.

33:40.700 --> 33:42.140
She refused to see you

33:42.720 --> 33:44.320
not because she is mad at you.

33:45.910 --> 33:47.710
She's just very upset right now.

33:48.240 --> 33:49.640
There are certain things

33:49.960 --> 33:52.050
she can't bring herself to say to you.

33:52.110 --> 33:53.570
I hope you can understand.

33:54.250 --> 33:56.100
As for the competition,

33:56.570 --> 33:57.970
that's her own business.

33:58.770 --> 34:00.610
You can't impose your ideas

34:00.960 --> 34:01.920
on her,

34:02.000 --> 34:03.060
and neither can we.

34:06.380 --> 34:07.010
Shengli,

34:08.880 --> 34:10.590
y-you're a nice young man.

34:12.630 --> 34:14.590
Your love for Zhuang Zhuang is genuine.

34:14.590 --> 34:16.170
I bet you can also feel

34:16.520 --> 34:18.520
that her love for you is genuine too.

34:20.230 --> 34:20.830
That said,

34:21.550 --> 34:23.949
you should show some understanding for us.

34:29.460 --> 34:30.380
Although Zhuang Zhuang is not

34:30.380 --> 34:31.780
my biological daughter,

34:31.900 --> 34:33.530
she's the only child I have,

34:33.900 --> 34:35.500
and I see her as my own.

34:36.130 --> 34:37.300
I've come to an age

34:38.000 --> 34:39.330
where I'd hate to see her

34:39.409 --> 34:41.590
drifting around out there all the time.

34:41.590 --> 34:42.639
On this point,

34:42.840 --> 34:44.969
I think your parents feel the same way.

34:46.610 --> 34:47.320
Mr. Ye,

34:48.010 --> 34:49.340
I don't know what exactly

34:49.340 --> 34:51.070
has gone wrong between me and her.

34:51.070 --> 34:51.670
Neither do I think

34:51.670 --> 34:52.420
anything has gone wrong

34:52.420 --> 34:53.480
between me and her.

34:54.210 --> 34:54.880
We've stayed

34:54.880 --> 34:55.760
and struggled for so long in Beijing

34:55.760 --> 34:57.420
just to realize our dreams, right?

34:57.420 --> 34:58.730
She's very close to achieving hers now.

34:58.730 --> 34:59.440
Her dream

34:59.440 --> 35:01.100
is only one step away from her.

35:01.110 --> 35:02.920
The result really doesn't matter.

35:02.920 --> 35:04.780
At least she should give it a shot.

35:05.190 --> 35:07.050
I understand what you're saying.

35:07.980 --> 35:09.170
But reality...

35:09.860 --> 35:11.690
isn't as simple as you think.

35:14.210 --> 35:15.540
Speaking of reality...

35:17.940 --> 35:19.420
we don't define

35:19.510 --> 35:20.670
a good life

35:20.730 --> 35:21.940
as having much money

35:22.280 --> 35:23.460
and many houses.

35:23.860 --> 35:24.440
However,

35:25.420 --> 35:27.100
Zhuang Zhuang's mother and I

35:29.090 --> 35:32.010
both hope her future life

35:32.190 --> 35:33.670
can be stable and secure.

35:34.730 --> 35:36.390
That's also part of the reason

35:36.650 --> 35:38.580
for her quitting the competition.

35:40.050 --> 35:42.570
She needs to figure out for herself

35:43.470 --> 35:45.270
which path to take in the future.

35:46.340 --> 35:49.730
Both of you need some alone time.

35:53.420 --> 35:53.950
Shengli,

35:55.840 --> 35:59.360
you are at an age to hustle and grind.

35:59.530 --> 36:01.190
you should focus on doing well

36:01.420 --> 36:02.750
with the things at hand.

36:03.360 --> 36:04.880
As for everything else,

36:05.570 --> 36:08.530
leave it to time and fate.

37:10.090 --> 37:11.150
[Prosperity]

37:11.150 --> 37:14.370
[Hostel]

37:12.170 --> 37:12.780
Ma'am?

37:14.320 --> 37:15.510
Ma'am, I need a room.

37:16.210 --> 37:17.210
For how many days?

37:17.550 --> 37:19.240
Well... three.

37:20.420 --> 37:21.070
Your ID?

37:36.320 --> 37:37.780
Ma'am, can I use the phone?

37:38.260 --> 37:38.780
Sure.

37:38.900 --> 37:40.650
30 cents a minute for local calls,
and 60 for long-distance ones.

37:40.650 --> 37:42.190
Okay, this call is going to Beijing.

37:42.190 --> 37:42.590
Okay.

37:53.300 --> 37:53.570
Hello?

37:53.570 --> 37:54.300
Hello, Manager.

37:54.300 --> 37:55.230
This is Shengli.

37:55.730 --> 37:57.300
Shengli, where are you?

37:57.380 --> 37:58.240
I'm in Wenzhou.

37:59.050 --> 38:00.650
Director Weng is in trouble.

38:00.840 --> 38:01.630
His house under mortgage

38:01.630 --> 38:03.360
has been auctioned by the bank.

38:10.470 --> 38:11.760
My old house...

38:13.120 --> 38:15.650
was auctioned off for over 900,000 yuan.

38:16.400 --> 38:17.650
The 500,000 I owed the bank

38:17.650 --> 38:18.650
has been paid off.

38:18.800 --> 38:20.050
The rest of the money

38:20.050 --> 38:20.880
is in this passbook.

38:20.880 --> 38:23.190
The police have already caught
the culprit.

38:23.190 --> 38:25.320
Although he has squandered
the money,

38:25.320 --> 38:28.110
it's not entirely impossible
to make him compensate.

38:28.110 --> 38:29.530
This won't do, Director Weng.

38:29.530 --> 38:31.030
I can't let you pay for everything alone.

38:31.030 --> 38:31.980
I'll work something out.

38:31.980 --> 38:33.040
No, don't.

38:33.150 --> 38:35.550
I'll by no means let you bear the debt.

38:37.130 --> 38:39.530
Besides, I introduced that guy
to the crew.

38:39.530 --> 38:40.990
I'm also feeling terrible

38:41.300 --> 38:43.160
about how things have turned out.

38:44.590 --> 38:46.900
Plus, you don't have any money.

38:48.000 --> 38:49.390
Anyway, no matter what,

38:49.460 --> 38:50.050
we

38:50.050 --> 38:51.170
did this together.

38:51.530 --> 38:53.860
So I should take half the responsibility.

39:29.760 --> 39:31.740
[The Late Love]

39:32.470 --> 39:33.610
[The Late Love]

39:39.300 --> 39:40.100
Put it inside.

39:40.380 --> 39:40.800
Okay.

39:40.900 --> 39:41.510
How's the flavor?

39:41.510 --> 39:42.420
Good, huh?

39:42.420 --> 39:43.150
Pretty nice.

39:49.950 --> 39:51.410
Too cramp up there, right?

40:01.940 --> 40:02.760
Buddy,

40:02.790 --> 40:05.120
you're reselling goods in Russia, right?

40:14.260 --> 40:17.830
-Welcome!
-Warm welcome!

40:17.980 --> 40:21.870
-Congratulations!
-Heartfelt congratulations!

40:21.900 --> 40:23.760
Winter in Beijing is really long.

40:24.750 --> 40:26.660
Spring is approaching, isn't it?

40:27.710 --> 40:28.530
Shengli,

40:29.650 --> 40:31.770
Zhuang Zhuang can't go with you.

40:32.170 --> 40:33.980
Zhuang Zhuang's mother and I

40:35.890 --> 40:37.030
both hope

40:37.430 --> 40:38.620
her future life

40:39.090 --> 40:40.530
can be stable and secure.

40:41.430 --> 40:42.910
That's part of the reason

40:43.460 --> 40:45.390
for her quitting the competition.

40:46.900 --> 40:49.620
She needs to figure out for herself

40:50.400 --> 40:52.200
which path to take in the future.

40:53.360 --> 40:56.460
Both of you need some alone time.

41:12.450 --> 41:15.210
[Central TV & Radio Tower;
altitude: 405 meters]

41:32.000 --> 41:33.670
The surgery was very successful.

41:33.670 --> 41:35.580
The patient can be transferred
to a regular ward tonight.

41:34.420 --> 41:39.630
[No smoking in public areas]

41:36.460 --> 41:37.400
Every time you turn her over,

41:37.400 --> 41:38.840
check on the drainage tube.

41:38.840 --> 41:40.320
If the fluid turns bright red,

41:40.320 --> 41:41.690
the volume suddenly increases,

41:41.690 --> 41:43.130
or the flow is blocked by blood clots,

41:43.130 --> 41:44.430
turn to a nurse immediately.

41:44.390 --> 41:49.040
[No smoking in public areas]

41:44.570 --> 41:45.880
Okay. Thanks for your hard work.

41:45.880 --> 41:46.340
Thank you.

41:46.340 --> 41:47.000
No problem.

41:49.380 --> 41:51.180
I'll watch your mother tonight.

41:51.570 --> 41:53.260
You haven't slept for days.

41:53.320 --> 41:54.320
Go get some sleep.

41:54.380 --> 41:55.980
Try not to worry your mother.

41:56.960 --> 41:58.760
I want to make a trip to Shanghai.

41:59.400 --> 42:01.800
You still want to find a specialist
for her?

42:01.960 --> 42:02.690
My mom already has

42:02.690 --> 42:03.940
underlying endocrine conditions

42:03.940 --> 42:06.400
that'll affect her recovery after surgery.

42:07.190 --> 42:09.330
I'm worried that missing
the best recovery window

42:09.330 --> 42:11.860
will increase her risk
of cancer recurrence.

42:12.210 --> 42:14.340
We need to get her in a better hospital.

42:16.550 --> 42:16.960
Okay.

42:17.480 --> 42:18.080
Thank you.

42:19.730 --> 42:21.390
Sweaters, quality sweaters!

42:21.960 --> 42:23.090
Quality sweaters!

42:23.900 --> 42:24.570
This is good stuff.

42:24.570 --> 42:25.280
Are you Chinese?

42:25.280 --> 42:27.010
This is pretty. Why not buy one?

42:27.880 --> 42:28.810
Lower the price?

42:29.110 --> 42:31.240
I'm already selling at the cost price.

42:36.500 --> 42:36.920
This.

42:37.860 --> 42:38.420
H-How about this one?

